  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook the lamination puff according to package instructions.",
    "In a large pan, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add frozen seafood mix and cook until thawed.",
    "Season with Croatian paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "To assemble the lasagna, layer cooked lamination puff, seafood mixture, and repeat.",
